|2 |  MERGE DISTINCT|              |1        |40  |
|3 |   SORT         |              |1        |40  |
|4 |    TABLE SCAN  |t1            |1        |39  |
|5 | TABLE SCAN     |t2            |4        |37  |
===================================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([t2.c]), filter(nil), 
      equal_conds([t2.c = SUBQUERY_TABLE.a]), other_conds(nil)
  1 - output([SUBQUERY_TABLE.a]), filter(nil), 
      access([SUBQUERY_TABLE.a])
  2 - output([t1.a]), filter(nil), 
      distinct([t1.a])
  3 - output([t1.a]), filter(nil), sort_keys([t1.a, ASC])
  4 - output([t1.a]), filter([t1.a < 5]), 
      access([t1.a]), partitions(p0)
  5 - output([t2.c]), filter(nil), 
      access([t2.c]), partitions(p0)

explain 
select * from t2 
  where c in (select a from (select a from t1 where a<5) as t);
